channel.title: Looking for a developer - new project - lots of content - asap
channel.description:
Hi everyone,
I am looking for a developer for a new 317 RSPS project. The developer does not have to be experienced, our server has great ideas planned and will be 100% the more content packed server there ever was. I do not care about the income; you will receive a larger percentile of the profit that is made.
PM me your skype if you're interested in taking part of this project.
Kind regards,
